<h1> Instance for everyone </h1>
<h2> Instance is for everyone in every country, especially for Singapore. Singlish and other non-official languages are allowed on this instance. </h2>
<h1> Federate this instance!</h1>
<p> Start federating and remote following <a href="https://reveal.today/@owl">@owl</a></p>

<h1> Updates Philosophy </h1>
<p>In order to maintain a good instance and server integrity, we will upgrade the server when there is a major upgrade/release within 7 days of notice.</p>
<p>Any Github commits that are minor, and not a major release will be updated within 10 days of notice.</p>

<h1>Security</h1>
<p> We want to provide a safe environment for every one to use in this instance, any security issue alerted to us will  be dealt with seriously and in a timely manner. </p>
<p> We will not delete your data without your permission unless it is a server fault. All our administrators are carefully picked and trusted</p>
<p> Never give your passwords to anyone.</p>

<h1>Privacy</h1>
<p> You can choose to private your account under settings.</p>
<p> We will not give out any of your information even if you are deemed anonymous. We do not collect any of your data.</p>

<h1>Safe Community</h1>
<p> We want to establish a safe community for everyone. Any  obscene media (photos, gifs, videos) and posts should be reported. No pornographic material is allowed without "NSFW" tag in CW under your post box. Any religious, violence sensitive or related posts should be reported by the community. </p> 
<p> We will carefully monitor reported posts to ensure that this instance is safe for all audiences.</p></div>
